-- U.S. Lawmakers Are Said to Be Close to Deal on Payroll Tax-Cut Extension
-- B y   L a u r a   L i t v a n
-- 2011-12-22T20:39:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-22/u-s-lawmakers-are-said-to-be-close-to-deal-on-payroll-tax-cut-extension.html
U.S. lawmakers are close to an
agreement on a plan to continue a payroll-tax cut for two months
and require the Senate to appoint conference committee members
to negotiate with the House on a longer-term plan, a Republican
congressional aide said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
